name: BigFart
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: big fart
des: Introducing Big Fart, the ultimate Alexa skill for all your flatulence needs! Whether you're looking to make a hilarious prank, or just want to let off some steam, Big Fart has got you covered. With a wide variety of fart noises to choose from, you'll never run out of ways to make people laugh. From the classic 'toot' to the more exotic 'fizzle', Big Fart has it all. And with new sounds added regularly, the fun never has to stop. So why settle for a boring old fart when you can have a Big Fart? Try it now and unleash the power of flatulence at your command!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
